            "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/876133952/image_876133952.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt='Ronald Reagan\"s Star, Hollywood Walk of Fame - August 11th, 2017 - Hollywood Boulevard, Los Angeles, California, CA, USA' data-id=\"876133952\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1150px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/876133952/image_876133952.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/876133952/image_876133952.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/876133952/image_876133952.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/876133952/image_876133952.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/876133952/image_876133952.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/876133952/image_876133952.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/876133952/image_876133952.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/876133952/image_876133952.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">R Scapinello/iStock Editorial via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Intro</h2> <p>There is nothing but talk about tariffs, tariffs and more tariffs. At this point I hope everyone has realized that in most cases they are ultimately paid by the end consumer, that is us, and not by foreign companies that want to export</p>",
